Class StrictLMTPDeliveryAgentConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.transport.impl.SMTPClientConfigImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SMTPDeliveryAgentConfig, SMTPClientConfig

    public class StrictLMTPDeliveryAgentConfig
extends SMTPDeliveryAgentConfigImpl
    LMTP-Servers MUST support PIPELINING according the RFC. So this configuration force them todo so by return PipeliningMode#DEPEND via the getPipeliningMode() method.
    Author:
    Maurer
